## 📌 Overview

A **Java console-based application** designed to manage student records efficiently.
The system supports **student creation, course enrollment, searching, and sorting using custom Comparator logic**.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

* ➕ Add multiple students dynamically
* 📚 Enroll students in multiple courses
* 🔍 Search student using unique ID
* 📊 Sort students by name using `Comparator`
* 🖥️ Display structured student data

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

* Java
* OOP (Encapsulation, Abstraction)
* Collections Framework (`ArrayList`)
* Comparator & Sorting
* Scanner (User Input Handling)

---

## 🎯 ATS Keywords

Java, OOP, Collections Framework, ArrayList, Comparator, Sorting Algorithms, Data Structures, Console Application, Object-Oriented Design, Clean Code, Exception Handling, CLI Application, Java Development

